'''2010年西孟加拉邦列车脱轨事故'''发生于2010年5月28日，地点位于[[印度|印度]][[西孟加拉邦|西孟加拉邦]][[西密德纳坡|西密德纳坡]]，原因是部分[[路轨|路轨]]被拆去而导致列车[[脫軌|脫軌]]。它造成了超过138人死亡，約200人受傷，其中30多人重傷。<ref name=HT28May201068killed/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=235472 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-05-30 |archive-date=2018-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622083749/http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=235472 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 背景 ==
出軌事故發生於[[印度共产党（毛主义）|印度共产党（毛主义）]]在当地为期4天的总罢工开始后90分鐘<ref>{{cite web|url = http://english.aljazeera.net/news/asia/2010/05/201052804354131331.html|publisher = Al-Jazeera|title = 'Sabotage' behind India train crash|accessdate = 2010-05-28|date = 2010-05-28|archive-date = 2010-09-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100920051131/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/asia/2010/05/201052804354131331.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。事發時為「黑色週」，全國安保進入最高戒準狀態<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/world/la-fg-india-trains-20100528,0,6845745.story | work = Los Angeles Times | accessdate = 2010-05-28 | date = 2010-05-28 | title = India train crash leaves 65 dead in West Bengal state | first = Mark | last = Magnier | archive-date = 2010-05-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100528101435/http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/world/la-fg-india-trains-20100528,0,6845745.story | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

印度鐵路大臣在襲擊發生前數星期曾表示，由于[[印度共产党（毛主义）|印度共产党（毛主义）]]的大罢工和阻碍，印度鐵路遭受的損失已高達50億[[盧比|盧比]]。罢工以及其他威胁已對某些地区的客運和貨運造成不利影响<ref name="bizstand"/>。

== 出軌事故 ==
印度上午1時30分（UTC+5:30，下同），該列有13節車廂，從[[豪拉车站|豪拉]]開往[[孟買|孟買]]的載客列車，在駛至缺失路軌的路段時出軌<ref name=IndiaExpres28May2010FifteenDead/>。列車出軌後再與反方向駛至的載貨列相撞<ref name=IndiaExpres28May2010FifteenDead/>。救援人員在客車內救出26人，最少有71人死亡<ref name=HT28May201068killed/>。被移去的路軌位於Khemasoli與Sardiya站之間<ref name=IndiaExpres28May2010FifteenDead/>。除了路軌被移去，承托組件鱼尾板也發現鬆脫，表明受到蓄意破坏<ref name=BBC27May2010TwentyFiveDead/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://livestreamingx.com/gyaneshwari-express-accident-one-foot-section-of-track-missing-05282826.html |title=Gyaneshwari Express accident One foot section of track missing |accessdate=2010-05-29 |archive-date=2010-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100612013150/http://livestreamingx.com/gyaneshwari-express-accident-one-foot-section-of-track-missing-05282826.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

調查人員又發現有爆炸痕跡，未能確定事故有否涉及恐怖襲擊，鐵路大臣瑪瑪塔·班納芝（Mamata Banerjee）表示該爆炸是屬有預謀襲擊的一部分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ndtv.com/news/india/bomb-blast-caused-derailment-mamata-banerjee-28354.php |title=Bomb blast caused train derailment: Mamata Banerjee |publisher=Ndtv.com |date=2010-01-20 |accessdate=2010-05-28 |archive-date=2011-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110202085126/http://www.ndtv.com/news/india/bomb-blast-caused-derailment-mamata-banerjee-28354.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她說：「列車車長聽見爆炸聲，因此我們會從這方面著手調查。但我們已警覺是印度共產黨放置了爆炸裝置。」<ref name="bizstand"/>

== 救援工作 ==
[[印度空軍|印度空軍]]派出直升機協助把傷者送往醫院<ref name=BBC27May2010TwentyFiveDead/>。此外，一列醫療列車也被派到事發現場<ref name="NDTV"/>。

== 責任 ==
當地警察部長表示，印度共產黨把事發路段的一段長46公分的路軌移去，故須負上全責<ref name=BBC27May2010TwentyFiveDead/>{{无关引用}}。警方在現場發現毛派附属組織「對抗警察鎮壓人民委员会」（Police Santras Birodhi Janosadharan Committee，或People's Committee against Police Atrocities，缩写为PCPA）的声称对事件负责的海报。<ref name=BBC27May2010TwentyFiveDead/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://livestreamingx.com/gyaneshwari-express-accident-maoist-flag-found-05282829.html |title=Gyaneshwari Express accident maoist flag found |accessdate=2010-05-29 |archive-date=2012-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120724014512/http://www.livestreamingx.com/gyaneshwari-express-accident-maoist-flag-found-05282829.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>而PCPA发言人否认PCPA有参与。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/marxists-derailed-train-to-defame-us-pcpa/116623-37-64.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100531194206/http://ibnlive.in.com/news/marxists-derailed-train-to-defame-us-pcpa/116623-37-64.html|url-status=dead|archive-date=31 May 2010|title=Marxists derailed train to defame us: PCPA|date=30 May 2010}}</ref>當西孟加拉邦警方指事件極有可能是[[印度共产党（毛主义）|印度共产党（毛主义）]]策劃後，毛派发言人表示毛派对此没有任何参与。<ref name=BBC27May2010TwentyFiveDead/>

== 反應 ==
總理[[曼莫汉·辛格|曼莫汉·辛格]]向事故中的死者表示哀痛<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://livestreamingx.com/pm-expresses-grief-over-loss-of-lives-in-mishap-involving-gyaneshwari-express-05282818.html |title=PM expresses grief over loss of lives in mishap involving Gyaneshwari Express |accessdate=2010-05-29 |archive-date=2010-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100603053041/http://livestreamingx.com/pm-expresses-grief-over-loss-of-lives-in-mishap-involving-gyaneshwari-express-05282818.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並表示政府已向每名死者的親屬發放50萬盧布的賠償金，並會替他們尋找工作<ref name="NDTV">NDTV. 28 May 2010. 7:30.</ref>，西孟加拉邦政府更會全數支付死傷者的醫療費用<ref name=BBC27May2010TwentyFiveDead/>。

當鐵路大臣瑪瑪塔·班納芝得悉該段日子是黑色週，及政府已把保安級別提升至最高後，她隨即趕赴現場親自指揮救援<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.oneindia.in/2010/05/28/mamatarushes-to-mishap-spot-says-railways-aware-ofma.html |title=Mamata rushes to mishap spot, says Railways aware of Maoist Black Day - Oneindia News |publisher=News.oneindia.in |date=2007-10-30 |accessdate=2010-05-28 |archive-date=2014-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140602195835/http://news.oneindia.in/2010/05/28/mamatarushes-to-mishap-spot-says-railways-aware-ofma.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

財政大臣布拉納·穆赫芝（Pranab Mukherjee）和西孟加拉邦總理[[布達德夫·巴塔查爾吉|布達德夫·巴塔查爾吉]]（Buddhadeb Bhattacharya）也譴責是次襲擊<ref name="ndtv2">NDTV. 28 May 2010, 16:45 IST.</ref>。布打特·巴達察雅更表示會全力打擊毛派的恐怖主義，維護國家安全<ref>{{cite web |url=http://beta.thehindu.com/news/national/article440395.ece |title=The Hindu : News / National : Buddhadeb vows to fight Maoists |publisher=Beta.thehindu.com |date= |accessdate=2010-05-29 |archive-date=2010-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100820075042/http://beta.thehindu.com/news/national/article440395.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="bizstand">{{cite web |url=http://www.business-standard.com/india/news/naxals-menace-stalks-railways/396375/ |title=Naxals menace stalks Railways |publisher=Business-standard.com |date= |accessdate=2010-05-29 |archive-date=2012-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121004184611/http://www.business-standard.com/india/news/naxals-menace-stalks-railways/396375/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

